p>\n                   <p class=\"mb-0\"><img src=\"../shared/images/header_img01.png\" alt=\"New Graduate\"></p>\n                 </div>\n               </a>\n             </div>\n             <div class=\"header__globalNavi__item\">\n               <a href=\"../carrier/\" class=\"text-center\">\n                 <div class=\"\">\n                   <p class=\"mb-0\">キャリア採用情報</p>\n                   <p class=\"mb-0\"><img src=\"../shared/images/header_img02.png\" alt=\"New Graduate\"></p>\n                 </div>\n               </a>\n             </div>\n             <div class=\"header__globalNavi__item\">\n               <a href=\"../fukuri/\" class=\"text-center\">\n                 <div class=\"\">\n                   <p class=\"mb-0\">福利厚生</p>\n                   <p class=\"mb-0\"><img src=\"../shared/images/header_img03.png\" alt=\"New Graduate\"></p>\n                 </div>\n               </a>\n             </div>\n           </div>\n         </div>\n         <!-- pcヘッダー　ここまで -->\n\n       </div>\n       <!-- container -->\n     </div>\n     <!-- c-container-maxWidth -->\n   </div>\n   <!-- header__inner -->\n</header>\n    <div class=\"l-main welfare\">\n      <div class=\"c-container-maxWidth\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n\n          <div class=\"p-copy d-none d-md-block p-welfareCopy\">\n            <p class=\"p-copy__text p-welfareCopy__text\">わたしたちが求めるのは、<br>どんなことにも興味を持って一生懸命に楽しめる人。<br>そして、人・モノ・環境すべてに対してふれあいを大切にできる人。</p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"c-section\">\n            <div class=\"row p-welfareBorder\">\n              <div class=\"col-12 col-md-3 p-welfareBorder--above p-md-3\">\n                  <p class=\"p-welfareTitle\">福利厚生</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"col-12 col-md-9  p-md-3\">\n                <ul class=\"p-list p-list--mark p-welfareList\">\n                  <li>各種社会保険</li>\n                  <li>財形貯蓄</li>\n                  <li>企業年金（確定拠出年金、マッチング拠出）</li>\n                  <li>業務災害補償保険</li>\n                  <li>社宅・独身寮（当社保有以外にも借り上げ制度有り）</li>\n                  <li>借り上げ制度：転勤者に対して、法人契約した一般住宅を貸与する制度で、転勤による経済的負担を軽減します。</li>\n                  <li>育児短時間勤務（子供が小学4年生終期まで）</li>\n                  <li>帰省旅費支給（単身赴任者へ月2回交通費支給）</li>\n                  <li>社員旅行</li>\n                </ul>\n\n                <div class=\"row p-welfareHouse\">\n                  <div class=\"col-12 col-md-4 p-welfareHouse__item\">\n                    <div class=\"row flex-md-column align-items-end p-welfareHouse__item__inner\">\n                      <div class=\"col-7 col-md-12 p-welfareHouse__item__image\"><img src=\"../shared/images/welfare_img01.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                      <p class=\"mb-0 col-5 col-md-12 p-welfareHouse__item__text\">兵庫県三田市の<br class=\"d-block d-md-none\">独身寮</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"col-12 col-md-4 p-welfareHouse__item\">\n                    <div class=\"row flex-md-column align-items-end p-welfareHouse__item__inner\">\n                      <div class=\"col-7 col-md-12 p-welfareHouse__item__image\"><img src=\"../shared/images/welfare_img02.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                      <p class=\"mb-0 col-5 col-md-12 p-welfareHouse__item__text\">兵庫県三田市の<br class=\"d-block d-md-none\">社宅</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"col-12 col-md-4 p-welfareHouse__item\">\n                    <div class=\"row flex-md-column align-items-end p-welfareHouse__item__inner\">\n                      <div class=\"col-7 col-md-12 p-welfareHouse__item__image\"><img src=\"../shared/images/welfare_img03.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                      <p class=\"mb-0 col-5 col-md-12 p-welfareHouse__item__text\">東京都板橋区の<br class=\"d-block d-md-none\">独身寮</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--/l-main-->\n    <footer class=\"l-footer\">\r\n  <div class=\"footer__inner\">\r\n    <div class=\"c-container-maxWidth\">\r\n      <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"footer__item\">\r\n          <p class=\"footer__item__logo mb-0\"><a href=\"../../\"><img src=\"../shared/images/footer_logo.png\" alt=\"大成機工株式会社\"></a></p>\r\n          <p class=\"footer__item__siteName mb-0\"><a href=\"../\"><img src=\"../shared/images/footer_recruit.png\" alt=\"Recruit Special Site\"></a></p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <p class=\"footer__copyright\">Copyright © <span id=\"js-year\"></span> TAISEI KIKO Co., ltd. All Rights Reserved.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</footer>\r\n\r\n<!-- ページトップここから -->\r\n<div id=\"page-top\"><a href=\"#\"><img src=\"../shared/images/img_pageTop.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"\"></a></div>\r\n<!-- ページトップここまで -->\r\n  </div>\n  <!--/p-wrapper-->\n  <!--▼▼共通JS（フッター）▼▼-->\r\n<script src=\"//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js\"></script> \r\n<script src=\"../shared/js/include.js\"></script>\r\n<!--▲▲共通JS（フッター）▲▲-->\r\n</body>\n\n</html>\n","finalUrl":"https://www.taiseikiko.com/recruit/fukuri/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T16:51:00.395Z"}